      <title>香港法院责令中国恒大清算</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院周一下令对中国恒大集团进行清算，此举可能会在中国摇摇欲坠的金融市场中引发连锁反应，因为政策制定者正忙于遏制日益加深的危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrande-ordered-liquidate-by-hong-kong-court-2024-01-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 03:55:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
